data.description: Welcome home to Hawkins Cove in desirable Intracoastal West. This 4b/2ba home has been completely updated and shows like a model home. Boasting an open floorplan with a formal dining and formal living space, these are the perfect flex spaces to fit your needs. New interior and exterior paint, LVP flooring, custom cabinets with quartz countertops and luxurious renovated bathrooms are just a few of the amazing features of this home. New windows in 2018 and roof in 2019. The backyard is spacious, fully fenced and features a covered lanai perfect for entertaining and plenty of space for grilling, too. This home is centrally located to the Beaches, downtown Jacksonville, the St. Johns Town Center, UNF and Jacksonville's military bases. This home is truly turnkey and move-in ready!
